Notes: WU #3 in WBCA/ESPN/USA Today Coaches Poll. Lady Blues win 22nd straight over
Bearcats in Lee Arena. Brooke Ubelaker leads WU with 18 points on 7 of 11
shooting. Corkey Stiger has 14 and Amanda Holmes has 6th double double of the
season and 2nd straight with 10 points and 13 rebounds.
Game.Officials: Randy Dillon,  Mark Wallace,  Robyn Wesibrook
